{"tid":250701,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"個mon冇野顯示出黎 求救 （新手","createTime":"2017-05-20T09:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T11:30:35.000Z","uid":65525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e91af9bfa604f93e292f3ed64eb474e36525aea","tid":250701,"uid":65525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T09:41:14.000Z","msg":"果日我底版燒左，我去換過塊新嘅。跟住起我個fd屋企開機，跟住佢幫我超頻少少。果陣咩事都冇照開機挽<br />\n<br />\n跟住返到屋企開機果陣個mon平時無野出黎會有舊寫住｛無顯示｝嘅野出黎。跟住今次一開機果陣一開始係寫｛無顯示｝，但等一陣佢就轉左｛超頻｝兩隻字之後一定除左呢兩隻字乜都冇<br />\n<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n起個fd屋企駁個mon果條線係hdmi ,我屋企係vga <br />\n<br />\n唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b56d417e0189d43fadcbe96bb3250b9b15eb147","tid":250701,"uid":49109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T09:48:38.000Z","msg":"咁你都轉番hdmi試下囉"},{"pid":"e198cbcbed9f23fffaaa4e10de16a441e8d265fc","tid":250701,"uid":65525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T09:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你都轉番hdmi試下囉</blockquote><br />\n我個mon得vga同白色果個插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5498c866ed0e4d1b7f1f69bed9933486a12559","tid":250701,"uid":26030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:04:41.000Z","msg":"挽你老母<br />\n識搞都唔幫你"},{"pid":"f02defb870750382bf4c63e39ebf5accc8b8ac84","tid":250701,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:09:31.000Z","msg":"挽你老母"},{"pid":"9e0fece140c9812402d3280c32d18c295181cb4b","tid":250701,"uid":106598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:30:35.000Z","msg":"挽你老母"}]}